class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 23, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104udc1665702532677.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/udc1665702532677.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/udc1665702532677.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"udc1665702532677\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface</span> object enables you to obtain information about DSP instances.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"udc1665702532677__section_w223ab1b5b1_w224ab1b5_w225ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d269634e52\">Functions</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Data Addressing Functions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Function</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pic1665702532756.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pic1665702532756.html\" title=\"Returns the component name of this component instance, or the main component instance.\">getComponentName()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__2\">\n Returns the component name of the main <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gtd1665702532835.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gtd1665702532835.html\" title=\"Returns an array of uniface.Entity objects contained by the current object, or by the main instance.\">getEntities()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__2\">\n Returns an array of <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Entity</span> objects representing the outer entities of the main <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oel1665702532918.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oel1665702532918.html\" title=\"Get the named entity in the specified occurrence or component instance, or the main instance.\">getEntity()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__2\">\n Returns the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Entity</span> object that represents the named outer entity on the main <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jqg1665702532996.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqg1665702532996.html\" title=\"Returns an array of names of the component instances that are currently available on the browser.\">getInstanceNames()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__2\">\n Returns an alphabetically-sorted array holding the names of all component instances that are accessible on the web page. The returned array always contains at least one component instance name (the outermost instance).\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xmp1665702533078.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmp1665702533078.html\" title=\"Returns a reference to the uniface.Instance object that represents a given DSP instance name on the browser.\">getInstance()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__2\">\n Returns the main JavaScript object, or an object of type <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span>, which gives access to selected properties of a component instance.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oxz1665702533153.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oxz1665702533153.html\" title=\"Holds the URL for the Uniface Web Application Server (WASV).\">wrdurl</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15029e1_d15030e1_d15031e1__entry__2\">\n Holds the base URL of the Web Request Dispatcher (WRD), which is the contact point for the Uniface backend. If not assigned, the default is used and <span class=\"keyword apiname\">wrdurl</span> is undefined.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15032e1_d15033e1_d15034e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">DSP Instance Functions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15032e1_d15033e1_d15034e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Function</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15032e1_d15033e1_d15034e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15032e1_d15033e1_d15034e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tle1665702533236.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tle1665702533236.html\" title=\"Asynchronously activates an operation on the current component instance, or the main instance.\">activate()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15032e1_d15033e1_d15034e1__entry__2\">\n Activate an operation or supported trigger on the main component instance. The called operation can be executed on the client or the server, depending on how it is declared.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15032e1_d15033e1_d15034e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dxn1665702533340.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dxn1665702533340.html\" title=\"Asynchronously creates a DSP component instance and executes the specified operation (if any).\">createInstance()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15032e1_d15033e1_d15034e1__entry__2\">\n Creates a new DSP instance that is added to the component instances accessible on the web page.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15032e1_d15033e1_d15034e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lnp1665702533422.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lnp1665702533422.html\" title=\"Removes a component instance from memory.\">remove</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_d15032e1_d15033e1_d15034e1__entry__2\">\n Deletes the specified DSP instance, its data, and all child DSP instances and their data.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"udc1665702532677__table_v35_lds_21c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Predefined values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"udc1665702532677__table_v35_lds_21c__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Function</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"udc1665702532677__table_v35_lds_21c__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_v35_lds_21c__entry__1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hjz1705997620702.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hjz1705997620702.html\" title=\"A predefined value for the properties of UX widgets, which is an instance of empty object, and is shown as an empty object {} in JavaScript debugger.\">RESET</a></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"udc1665702532677__table_v35_lds_21c__entry__2\">Predefined value for the properties of UX\n                        widgets.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"udc1665702532677__section_w226ab1b5b3_w227ab1b5_w228ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d269634e346\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"udc1665702532677__p_d125165e1_d125166e1_d125167e1\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface</span> object is the starting point for the JavaScript Data Addressing API.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"udc1665702532677__p_d125168e1_d125169e1_d125170e1\">It enables you to create, remove, and access <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> objects, and to concisely activate or access the <dfn class=\"term\">main instance</dfn>. This a <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> that is not contained by any other instance. Its component name is part of the page's URL, and its layout forms the HTML loaded by the browser. All other instances are either contained in a DSP container, or invisible.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"udc1665702532677__p_d125171e1_d125172e1_d125173e1\">If there is only one\n\t\t <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Instance</span> or you want to address the main instance, you can use the\n\t\t following operations on the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface</span> object directly:\n\t\t <span class=\"keyword apiname\">activate</span>, <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getComponentName</span>, <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getEntity</span>, and\n\t\t <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getEntities</span>. Thus:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">uniface.activate(args);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"udc1665702532677__p_d125174e1_d125175e1_d125176e1\">is a synonym for</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">uniface.getInstance().activate(args);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"udc1665702532677__section_w229ab1b5b5_w230ab1b5_w231ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d269634e402\">Constants for Object Types</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"udc1665702532677__p_d125180e1_d125181e1_d125182e1\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface</span> object also provides the following constants to denote the types of object used in the API:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"udc1665702532677__li_d45800e1_d45801e1_d45802e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.TYPE_DSPINSTANCE</span>\n\t\t\t for <code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dtg1665702533539.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dtg1665702533539.html\" title=\"The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents.\">uniface.Instance</a>\n</code> objects</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"udc1665702532677__li_d45803e1_d45804e1_d45805e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.TYPE_ENTITY</span> for\n\t\t\t <code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"reb1665702537007.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/reb1665702537007.html\" title=\"The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects.\">uniface.Entity</a>\n</code> objects</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"udc1665702532677__li_d45806e1_d45807e1_d45808e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.TYPE_OCCURRENCE</span> for\n\t\t\t <code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hfh1665702535808.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hfh1665702535808.html\" title=\"The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object.\">uniface.Occurrence</a>\n</code> objects</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"udc1665702532677__li_d45809e1_d45810e1_d45811e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.TYPE_FIELD</span> for\n\t\t\t <code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dlx1665702535259.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlx1665702535259.html\" title=\"The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence.\">uniface.Field</a>\n</code> objects</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532633\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532633\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uniface Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 23, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The uniface object enables you to obtain information about DSP instances. Functions Table 1. Data Addressing Functions Function Description getComponentName() Returns the component name of the main uniface.Instance . getEntities() Returns an array of uniface.Entity objects representing the outer entities of the main uniface.Instance . getEntity() Returns the uniface.Entity object that represents the named outer entity on the main uniface.Instance . getInstanceNames() Returns an alphabetically-sorted array holding the names of all component instances that are accessible on the web page. The returned array always contains at least one component instance name (the outermost instance). getInstance() Returns the main JavaScript object, or an object of type uniface.Instance , which gives access to selected properties of a component instance. wrdurl Holds the base URL of the Web Request Dispatcher (WRD), which is the contact point for the Uniface backend. If not assigned, the default is used and wrdurl is undefined. Table 2. DSP Instance Functions Function Description activate() Activate an operation or supported trigger on the main component instance. The called operation can be executed on the client or the server, depending on how it is declared. createInstance() Creates a new DSP instance that is added to the component instances accessible on the web page. remove Deletes the specified DSP instance, its data, and all child DSP instances and their data. Table 3. Predefined values Function Description RESET Predefined value for the properties of UX widgets. Description The uniface object is the starting point for the JavaScript Data Addressing API. It enables you to create, remove, and access uniface.Instance objects, and to concisely activate or access the main instance . This a uniface.Instance that is not contained by any other instance. Its component name is part of the page's URL, and its layout forms the HTML loaded by the browser. All other instances are either contained in a DSP container, or invisible. If there is only one uniface.Instance or you want to address the main instance, you can use the following operations on the uniface object directly: activate , getComponentName , getEntity , and getEntities . Thus: uniface.activate(args); Copy is a synonym for uniface.getInstance().activate(args); Copy Constants for Object Types The uniface object also provides the following constants to denote the types of object used in the API: uniface.TYPE_DSPINSTANCE for uniface.Instance objects uniface.TYPE_ENTITY for uniface.Entity objects uniface.TYPE_OCCURRENCE for uniface.Occurrence objects uniface.TYPE_FIELD for uniface.Field objects Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}